<p style="margin-left: 20px;">Offshore Development will cater to Fixed Bid (Turnkey) projects where the scope, requirement, development, testing, change management, sing-offs are fully defined and agreed.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong> Pure On Site:</strong>
<p style="margin-left: 20px;">On-Site model is preferred when requirement and scope is not well-defined. Task specific development, delivery and maintenance are done from Customer Site on T&amp;M basis.</p>
<p> </p>
</td>
